111
00:08:52,945 --> 00:08:53,833
Hell yeah.

112
00:08:55,846 --> 00:08:57,207
Hey, Max. How about coming over here?

113
00:08:57,207 --> 00:08:58,342
I just got a new FIFA game.

114
00:09:00,186 --> 00:09:01,121
