130
00:10:11,836 --> 00:10:13,285
Seems like a fun game.

131
00:10:14,496 --> 00:10:15,383
I see.

132
00:10:17,201 --> 00:10:18,000
Kang.

133
00:10:19,299 --> 00:10:22,869
