134
00:10:23,691 --> 00:10:25,801
Nobody likes being forced to do things they don't like.

135
00:10:26,076 --> 00:10:27,200
I understand.

136
00:10:29,065 --> 00:10:30,459
As far as I'm concerned, 

137
00:10:31,106 --> 00:10:34,428
